title: Ceph Storage: Pools
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the size and used space of pools of Ceph storage systems.

 The usage is checked values configurable using the ruleset "Filesystems (used space and growth)".

item:
 The pool name.

discovery:
 One service is created for each pool.

cluster:
 On a cluster only the first nodes' response is checked.
